msgstr "Chapter One"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thag1.2:4.1"
msgid "1.2. Mahākoṭṭhikattheragāthā"
msgstr "1.2. Mahākoṭṭhika"

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc2"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts2"></a>
msgctxt "thag1.2:5.1"
msgid "“Upasanto uparato,"
msgstr "Calm and quiet,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.2:5.2"
msgid "mantabhāṇī anuddhato;"
msgstr "thoughtful in counsel, and stable—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.2:5.3"
msgid "Dhunāti pāpake dhamme,"
msgstr "he shakes off bad qualities"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.2:5.4"
msgid "dumapattaṃva māluto”ti."
msgstr "as the wind shakes leaves off a tree."

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "thag1.2:6.1"
msgid ""
"Itthaṃ sudaṃ āyasmā <span class=\"var\" title=\"mahākoṭṭhito (bj, s2, s3) | "
"mahākoṭṭhika (pts1-2)\" id=\"note3\">mahākoṭṭhiko</span> thero gāthaṃ "
"abhāsitthāti."
msgstr ""
"It was thus that this verse was recited by the senior venerable Mahākoṭṭhika."
